ZH: 我昨天目击了一起车祸。
EN: I witnessed a car accident yesterday.

ZH: 他目击了一名女孩被偷走她的包包。
EN: He witnessed a girl getting her purse stolen.

ZH: 我无意中目击了他们之间的争吵。
EN: I accidentally witnessed their argument.

ZH: 这个地方安装了很多监控摄像头以便目击犯罪活动。
EN: This place has many surveillance cameras installed to witness criminal activities.

ZH: 我们需要目击者来证人这起事件。
EN: We need eyewitnesses to testify this incident.

ZH: 目击者描述了犯罪现场的细节。
EN: The eyewitness described the details of the crime scene.

ZH: 警方正在寻找目击者以协助调查。
EN: The police are looking for witnesses to assist in the investigation.

ZH: 我将会成为这场案件的目击证人。
EN: I will be the eyewitness of this case.

ZH: 他是唯一一个目击整个事件的人。
EN: He is the only person who witnessed the whole event.

ZH: 目击者的证词对于案件的审判非常关键。
EN: The testimony of the eyewitness is crucial for the trial.

ZH: 我通过这个窗户目击到了他们的秘密会议。
EN: I witnessed their secret meeting through this window.

ZH: 这位目击者已经被警方保护起来。
EN: The eyewitness has been placed under police protection.

ZH: 目击者的身份将保密。
EN: The identity of the eyewitness will be kept confidential.

ZH: 目击犯罪后，我立刻报了警。
EN: After witnessing the crime, I immediately called the police.

ZH: 目击者的话在法庭上被视为证据。
EN: The words of the eyewitness are considered evidence in the court.

ZH: 目击者提供了一个重要的线索来破案。
EN: The eyewitness provided a crucial clue to solve the case.

ZH: 他们找到了目击者所描述的嫌疑犯。
EN: They found the suspect described by the eyewitness.

ZH: 这个视频可以作为目击事件的证明。
EN: This video can serve as evidence of witnessing the incident.

ZH: 警方发布了寻找目击者的公告。
EN: The police issued a notice to find the eyewitness.

ZH: 如果你是目击者，请与警方联系。
EN: If you are an eyewitness, please contact the police.
